data.description: Spacious home, with just under 2 acres. Tucked back off the main road for plenty of privacy, in a very convenient location just outside Jefferson, and only 10 minutes to downtown West Jefferson. No Restrictions and no HOA. Private paved driveway, with very little grade leads you to the home towards the back of the property providing easy year round access. Low maintenance exterior with vinyl siding and very little grass to cut. Main level features spacious great room with stone fireplace, open kitchen/ dining area, with granite countertops, breakfast bar, newer stainless steel appliances, coffee/wet bar area and plenty of cabinets. Laundry room located just off the kitchen, washer and dryer are included. Primary Bedroom with en suite Bath, with WIC on main level as well.  Additional room on main level is utilized as a home office but could serve as a BR if desired, with additional full BA that can be accessed from living area for guests. Upstairs features 2 large guest bedrooms that share a full bath. Basement provides ton of storage and has a finished room and a full bath. Ideal set up for the teenager or family member who wants their own space. Basement garage as well as a 2 car carport provide plenty of parking space. Back deck is a great spot for outdoor gatherings and the hottub is included. 3BR septic permit but home has 5 rooms that would meet the requirement for bedrooms. See today
